---
Source:
  Title: Old Testament
Locus:
  Page: 40
  Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Cause
---
Whoso casteth a stone on high, casteth it on his own head. ...Whoso diggeth
a pit shall fall herein; and he that setteth a trap shall be taken therein.
He that worketh mischief, it shall fall upon him, and he shall not know
whence it cometh.
